{"type": "article", "id": 23037, "title": "小山沙发组", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-01T07:34:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702104514VTFlyKzcoZurXmCG.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/23000.html\">昨天介绍了法国品牌 smarin 的沙发dune</a>，他们最新推出的也是像小山一样的沙发组。它有 8 个几何组件，都是用羊毛制成的，其中 4 种是方形的底座，任意放上三角形或梯形的靠背。不用的时候，靠墙排成连绵起伏的小山丘，可以随意拿走一块作为靠垫，是放在商务空间里的很好的装饰。售价 216 欧元起，<a href=\"http://shop.smarin.net/en/61-shapes\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104511ovLfqmlBPczk9h8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104511Nwf4En1UOkRVaMvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104512ZcYU57Kur6MPvTSs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104513N2zCP3haEFWljRvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}